ReturnPolicy.Description:
If you received your product and you don't like it for ANY reason, within 14 days after its receipt send it back to us and you'll get 100% refund. You need to enclose the postal slip which certifies the date when you received it and a copy of the postal receipt which certifies the date when you sent it back to us. You need to pay the shipping cost. The item must not be damaged or wear any tracks of use. The refund is made upon our receipt of the item.

If through our fault the product does not correspond to your order, we will sort it out asap at our expense.  We will replace the bad item with a good one or refund to you its full price if:

- you received a wrong item
- item you received is defective

In order to raise a claim, first you need to send us high quality photos of the bad item, showing the problem. Then you should send the item back to us, we make the refund or correct/replace it and send it back to you (everything at our cost).

If you received an item which was evidently damaged during the transportation, please immediately raise a claim to the post service which delivered it.
